cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1440\" data-pswp-width=\"2560\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The main character in Avowed, looking at the way to reach the Dead Man’s Mail treasure\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-6.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Obsidian Entertainment/Xbox Game Studios via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eWalk along the ramparts, turn left, and use lockpicks to open the chest and find \u003cstrong\u003eNecropants \u003c/strong\u003einside.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"dead-man-s-mail-reward\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eDead Man’s Mail reward\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1440\" data-pswp-width=\"2560\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A menu image showing the main character in Avowed wearing Necropants, the Dead Man’s Mail treasure reward\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-dead-mans-mail-treasure-map-location-solution-7.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Obsidian Entertainment/Xbox Game Studios via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eDespite the wizard boasting about creating a full set of deathly armor in the map description, the \u003cstrong\u003eNecropants \u003c/strong\u003eare the only treasure here. They come with a curious mix of stats that penalize essence, but offer good damage reduction.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNecropants stats\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15% damage reduction\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+39 additional damage reduction\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-25 maximum stamina\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-35 maximum essence\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNecropants enchantment\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSpectral Slave: Summons a spectre to fight alongside you\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePoison-Proofed: Grants +30 resistance to poison accumulation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eSummons in battle make excellent distractions to keep enemy attention off you and your companions, and if you sold your body to Elia in Emerald Stair, you can use the Revenant Collar’s skill to summon a revenant alongside the spectre. Poison resistance is also very useful, given how common Dreamthrall enemies are from here on out.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more treasure maps in the Shatterscarp region, see our solutions to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/525646\"\u003eSeafarer’s Boots\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/525549\"\u003eRobe of the Arcane Cheater\u003c/a\u003e treasure maps. And don’t miss our full \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/522871/walkthrough-main-story-all-missions-list\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eAvowed\u003c/em\u003e walkthrough\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
